I'm a **Systems Analysis and Development** student at **UNINTER**, focused on starting my career as a **Junior Java Backend Developer**.

I build portfolio projects centered on **Java and Spring Boot**, with emphasis on REST APIs, data validation, authentication, relational databases, and application deployment.

